"     </b>",
"     (Podofilox External)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     0.5% (3.5 mL): $99.48",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"list fbnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F210942\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
