"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?22/34/23076/abstract/8\">",
"      Komamura K, Shannon RP, Ihara T, et al. Exhaustion of Frank-Starling mechanism in conscious dogs with heart failure. Am J Physiol 1993; 265:H1119.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
